Amato et al. (2000), Bauer (1997), Duckworth (1998), Evans etal. (2000), Schaller &amp; Vrba (1996), Timmins et al. (1998), Timmins, Duckworth &amp; Long (2008c).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
